PLEASE UPDATE WHENEVER HARDWARE / CONTROL MAP CHANGES!

HARDWARE MAP
  Motor Controllers:
    - MCP1 = Motor controller plugged into port 6 of the core power module
    - MCP2 = Motor controller plugged into port 4 of the core power module
    - MCP3 = Motor controller plugged into port 3 of the core power module
  
  Motors: 
    - motorFrontR = Motor plugged into motor slot 1 of motor controller 1, front right wheel motor
    - motorFrontL = Motor plugged into motor slot 2 of motor controller 1, front left wheel motor
    - motorBack1 = Motor plugged into motor slot 1 of motor controller 2, back left wheel motor
    - motorBack2 = Motor plugged into motor slot 2 of motor controller 2, back right wheel motor
    - motorArm = Motor plugged into motor slot 1 of motor controller 3, arm motor 
  Servos:
    - 

CONTROL MAP
  Controller 1 (Driver 1):
    - Left Joystick = controls the left side wheel speed.
    - Right Joystick = controls the right side wheel speed.
    
  Controller 2 (Driver 2):
    - Left Joystick = controls arm direction 
